### Create a new entity
POST http://localhost:8080/restapi/Regions
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "id": 60,
  "regionName": "Alberta"
}

### GET All entity from REST API endpoint
GET http://localhost:8080/restapi/Regions

### GET One entity from REST API endpoint
GET http://localhost:8080/restapi/Regions/60

### UPDATE entity at the REST API endpoint - will replace all properties with the properties in the request body
PUT http://localhost:8080/restapi/Regions/60
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "id": 60,
  "regionName": "51st USA State"
}

### DELETE entity at the REST API endpoint
DELETE http://localhost:8080/restapi/Regions/60
